CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 1, 1953, pg. 12 reads: "Annual Breakfast Is Gala - The gala annual breakfast given by the smart Min-Ceil Club on the lawn of the Emmett Davises of Lincoln Avenue, draw its usual socialite group of guests. Some snapped here include,...Right photo: George Brown, Mrs. Julia Calloway and Mrs. Mary Holloman chat together. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of George Brown, Julia Calloway, and Mary Holloman, seated at table for the Min-Ceil Club's annual breakfast on lawn of the Emmett Davises, Lincoln Avenue
